{"tid":189847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【冷漠世界】乘客個頭被夾住 月台人來人往但無人施救","createTime":"2017-04-06T17:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T02:37:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd1a27192a2b4e1bf82408601f01f4d51970f09","tid":189847,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170406/large/1491451124_c0a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170406%2Flarge%2F1491451124_c0a9.jpg&h=4e994e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國紐約市一名婦人搭地鐵時不幸被車門夾頭，但幾名途人對她的情況視而不見走過，其中一人更是大都會運輸局（MTA）職員，途人的冷漠令人側目。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的短片可見，一名婦人被列車車門夾住頸部，身體仍被困在車內，她未有大聲求救，而且看來也沒有驚慌失措。拍片者身在另一面月台的列車上，片中可見當時車站月台上人來人往，背景中僅得另一名女性大叫的聲音，要人立即打開車門。<br />\n當時月台上亦有其他途人，但至少有5人經過時，對被車門夾住的婦人視而不見，沒有停下來幫忙，其中一名途人甚至穿上大都會運輸局的制服。<br />\n目前未知事件發生在哪一個車站，亦不清楚該名婦人被困多久或者有沒有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170407/56527706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170407%2F56527706&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=5eb3c7e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170407%2F56527706&h=2535474e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170407/56527706</a>"},{"pid":"57612710e69745841dc4086db538d54165830d1d","tid":189847,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:18:09.000Z","msg":"渣嫁"},{"pid":"1cd3ca31536a7d481d0318e3ed4e2a5addf70940","tid":189847,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"第一次估錯國家"},{"pid":"c69e3cbe308a191791b1c7d7a9de2b172af36b70","tid":189847,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src